What you need !
***************

   - Kickstart >= 2.0

   - Workbench >= 2.0

   - UMS (Universal Message System) >= v11 (see: @{"References" Link "References"})

   - Several additions in 'ums.config' (see: @{"Installation" Link "Installation"})


